Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.94,0:01:14.73,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}I love you from my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.88,0:01:20.33,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}I love you forever with you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.92,0:01:38.82,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}每日从早到晚 你都在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.94,0:01:43.38,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}这样的生活不断重复
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.85,0:01:46.47,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}一觉醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.62,0:01:48.98,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}你已泡好热咖啡等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:53.56,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}紧紧抱住你的左臂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.75,0:01:58.65,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}以前曾屈指等待你的出现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.72,0:02:03.74,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}如今见到你的时间是越来越多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.89,0:02:08.05,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,150)\be1}这样的幸福谁曾料到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.07,0:02:13.66,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,200)\be1}你和我 都堕入了爱河
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.77,0:02:18.58,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.72,0:02:21.96,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}初次体会到的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.30,0:02:26.11,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Oh 我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.22,0:02:28.84,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}永远永远
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.98,0:02:33.70,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}此情不变
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------EDCN2-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.76,0:23:36.72,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}为何 为何
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.88,0:23:41.89,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}我会如此心痛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.14,0:23:47.85,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}嘴上说 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.16,0:23:51.44,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}故作冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.40,0:23:53.93,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}嚣张的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.42,0:23:56.00,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}背后是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.37,0:24:00.53,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\be1}最大程度的逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.06,0:24:06.18,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}为什么呢 泪水不断涌出
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.30,0:24:12.96,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\be1}不敢正视他的容颜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.91,0:24:16.60,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}明天一定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.83,0:24:18.45,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}比昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.58,0:24:23.29,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}想比朋友关系更进一步
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.32,0:24:24.96,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}明天一定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.14,0:24:26.80,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}梦里也一定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.89,0:24:30.58,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}恋爱之情更为闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.75,0:24:32.56,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}Just a friend
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.69,0:24:34.62,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}Such a friend
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.78,0:24:37.54,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,400)\be1}Still a friend
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.01,0:24:45.00,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}为何 为何
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.19,0:24:50.00,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}I can't tell you my heart
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------PREV-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.38,0:00:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后啊 哥们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.43,0:00:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会对她说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.55,0:00:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「尽管外面冷彻骨髓」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.81,0:00:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我的心头却如此温暖」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.30,0:00:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「这一切 只因有你」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.32,0:00:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸如此类的话啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.77,0:00:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随后我会默不作声地牵起她的手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.94,0:00:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉向我的胸襟 按在胸口
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.18,0:00:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 哥们 你有在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.10,0:00:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…你在说圣诞约会的事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.79,0:00:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.00,0:00:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过在此之前 约会的对象要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.66,0:00:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠 一点破不就说不下去了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.70,0:00:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 你跟棚町进展如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.52,0:00:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前阵子 她无故缺席那时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.58,0:00:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听田中说 你拼了命到处找她哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.85,0:00:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说吧 进展如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.04,0:00:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…也没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.59,0:00:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.25,0:00:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你问我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.37,0:00:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如主动去约他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.56,0:00:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是个难得的大事件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.49,0:01:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.76,0:01:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就到了呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTA-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.98,0:02:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.90,0:02:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.58,0:02:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被纸割破手指啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.21,0:02:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你有没止血贴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.46,0:02:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 没
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.91,0:02:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.99,0:02:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没止血贴的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.28,0:02:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.81,0:02:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.10,0:03:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快…快给我止血贴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.51,0:03:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fs20\fsp-1\b0}（再不快点就要死啦 好疼）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.51,0:03:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿你没办法 知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.73,0:03:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮你去保健室拿就是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.50,0:03:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 哥们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺开心的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.59,0:03:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是发生了什么有趣的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.48,0:03:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就会发生了 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.45,0:03:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 快到圣诞了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.88,0:03:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 田中～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.11,0:03:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要得寸进尺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.92,0:03:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然没戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 缝裙子缝裙子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.03,0:03:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打搅了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.14,0:03:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是 欢迎来到保健室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为是惠子 为啥是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.27,0:03:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.52,0:03:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿成这样干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.62,0:03:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.50,0:03:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.81,0:03:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那能不能拜托你干点活儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.20,0:03:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干活？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.06,0:03:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 梅原手指被纸割破了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.22,0:03:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正想要止血贴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:03:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 止血贴是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,止血贴在…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 一条够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.19,0:04:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来 为啥在学校穿成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.33,0:04:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才惠子说我裙子下摆破了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.95,0:04:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在帮我补呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此也不用…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.47,0:04:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天没体育课 也没带运动服来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.13,0:04:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好这套刚洗过的制服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在书包里面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.51,0:04:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了 梅原在等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.59,0:04:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.49,0:04:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咋了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.28,0:04:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说清楚点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.85,0:04:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就…呃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.78,0:04:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰 平安夜有没什么预定活动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.75,0:04:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.47,0:04:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今还说啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.83,0:04:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是跟你约会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:05:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫你一直不来约我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就自作主张加入日程了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.25,0:05:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.09,0:05:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.66,0:05:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 跟薰约好了平安夜去约会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.01,0:05:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在保健室看她穿家庭餐厅制服也挺新鲜的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用这么惊慌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是在想奇怪的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.58,0:05:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到惠子 叫她快点拿校服给我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.75,0:05:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 收到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞晚餐 到处都好贵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.32,0:05:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 圣诞节干什么都得花钱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.42,0:05:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说 处处都要比平时贵20%
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.59,0:05:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵20%？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.59,0:05:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 在圣诞节约会的人也真够惨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.89,0:05:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.94,0:06:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 跟老哥也没啥关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.45,0:06:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.36,0:06:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年…哼哼 今年我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,435)\fs22}今年 今年我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 难道刚才吃的肉包子…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.84,0:06:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想豁出去买件新的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在平安夜 而且还是初次约会哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服是很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.35,0:06:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是买决胜内裤吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.52,0:06:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 我在想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是已经决定了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.93,0:06:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想跟纯一去「那里」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.75,0:06:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备工作很顺利嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.56,0:06:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 虽然出了些问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.73,0:06:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没影响
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.96,0:06:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参加市民集市的人数也增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这创设祭是一年比一年盛大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.70,0:07:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,执行委员长 辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 这话说得有点早了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 给我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.31,0:07:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因为小逢等会儿来不了我家的派对嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 我也送你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.17,0:07:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 不过我什么都没准备
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.98,0:07:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.11,0:07:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想去圣诞派对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.47,0:07:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天再办一场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.33,0:07:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是平安夜 但也是圣诞节啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.40,0:07:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦对了 要不要吃了游泳部的杂烩再走？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.52,0:07:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.32,0:07:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.19,0:07:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萝卜是我弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.37,0:07:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天就开始炖了 很入味哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 为茶会派传单吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.76,0:07:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对 梨穗子 就拜托你做宣传了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.21,0:07:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你带来客源
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.27,0:07:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我明白啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子 套上这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.42,0:07:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注目度必定上升
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.68,0:08:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过以她的性格嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.75,0:08:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟到十分二十分也是预料之中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到等了她半小时以上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.74,0:08:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会不来吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.44,0:08:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会又像两年前那样被放鸽子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 唯独薰不会做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.40,0:08:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙就算迟到也一定会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…应该
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.12,0:08:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.34,0:09:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了 太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.12,0:09:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底干啥去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.71,0:09:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 花太多功夫了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把功夫花在准时赴约上行不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.10,0:09:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都跟你道歉了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是道个歉就算完事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.52,0:09:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀别生气啦 心情好起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没生气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.14,0:09:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是担心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.64,0:09:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为你不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.12,0:09:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这绝对不会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.11,0:09:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么会做你讨厌的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 这是珍贵的初次约会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开心点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.52,0:09:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.77,0:09:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 笑一个～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 这个有点讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.18,0:09:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就别叫我笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错 这就像你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.34,0:09:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.11,0:10:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好啊…去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.36,0:10:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个地方想跟你去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.55,0:10:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.57,0:10:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里…是之前说的港塔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.52,0:10:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 近看果然好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我们赶紧登塔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.93,0:10:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登塔？登这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.49,0:10:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这儿有个公园
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如散个步
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.77,0:10:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正还有时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.74,0:10:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（讨厌 真色）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 像这样走在海边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会感觉很怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.39,0:10:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初中那时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们玩够了回家时 也是像这样走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了不少事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.61,0:10:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被梅原追
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.11,0:10:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一急 躲进了女厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.73,0:10:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上课时打瞌睡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.82,0:11:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸狠狠地撞到桌上 还流鼻血了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.77,0:11:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 薰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.24,0:11:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时应该说正经点的回忆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.66,0:11:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对 原本想耍我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果命根子挨踢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.01,0:11:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说的话 你这么好动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裙子飘得老高 啥都看光了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.72,0:11:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你偷看了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.79,0:11:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还坐我自行车后面 叫我送你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.15,0:11:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来 还摔过一次狠的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.78,0:11:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.43,0:11:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.16,0:11:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.89,0:11:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.79,0:11:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多到夜景漂亮的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.85,0:11:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都到这里了 当然要登塔咯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.51,0:11:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Comment: 0,0:00:03.00,0:00:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 我们上电梯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了 响
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.27,0:12:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这打扮是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.81,0:12:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是圣诞小姐选美比赛？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是已经结束了么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.03,0:12:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是结束了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.07,0:12:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿冠军的女生 说不能接受我不参赛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要跟我单挑来着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.92,0:12:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响 陪一下我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以是可以 这…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凹～凸～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.75,0:12:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尺寸不对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.41,0:12:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.70,0:12:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这太犯规了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各种意义上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.15,0:12:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你畏高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.63,0:12:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.97,0:12:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那过来这边看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.73,0:13:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿高处没辙啊 感觉风飕飕的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说我可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.71,0:13:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不看下面的话 这点程度…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.01,0:13:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 很努力嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.96,0:13:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好吧 这点算不了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 你不怕下面看到内…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.84,0:13:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 穿的是裤子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.25,0:13:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.01,0:13:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过看得见也没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可是穿了决胜内…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.98,0:13:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.86,0:13:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.37,0:13:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出局出局出局
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.43,0:13:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的畏高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样牵着手 感觉会好点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.84,0:13:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那暂时保持这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 薰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.91,0:14:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.64,0:14:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 雪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.57,0:14:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色圣诞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.06,0:14:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.18,0:14:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.81,0:14:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样俯视着雪飘落
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.46,0:14:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有点不可思议啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉赚到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.59,0:14:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种偶然 真的很少有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.23,0:14:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 有种要被吸进去的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.47,0:14:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.23,0:14:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 从高处看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.18,0:14:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会觉得这座城市很小
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.47,0:14:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我在这里出生 成长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.56,0:14:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.84,0:14:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在这里 堕入了爱河呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.02,0:15:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.39,0:15:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有话要跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.70,0:15:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,损友 伙伴 孽缘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.66,0:15:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表示我们之间关系的词多得是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.69,0:15:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我已经受不了这个距离了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.86,0:15:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.47,0:15:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于察觉到自己的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.76,0:15:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前都是拉着你到处冲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.52,0:15:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 那都是不久之前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉间 就被你吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.25,0:15:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为花了很长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.02,0:15:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,积累了一个又一个回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.39,0:15:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才会有这份感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.22,0:15:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能说出你100个缺点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.18,0:15:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 更能说出你101个优点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:15:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯一 我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.37,0:16:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.74,0:16:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真逊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.88,0:16:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在才发现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.96,0:16:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你说了不像你说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.64,0:16:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.84,0:16:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不嫌弃的话 我会一直待在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.19,0:16:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然之前一直都没挑明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我能满怀自信地说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.76,0:16:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我想永远跟薰在一起」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以跟你在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.61,0:16:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还有一句没说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.75,0:16:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.84,0:16:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也喜欢薰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.08,0:16:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.94,0:17:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 今天打搅了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.00,0:17:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.33,0:17:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 到我家的巴士已经没了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那来我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 老爸跟老妈去温泉旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.08,0:17:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有美也在家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.14,0:17:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 会添麻烦的 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.32,0:17:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会去家庭餐厅或者便利店打发时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.10,0:17:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.52,0:17:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没问题么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.32,0:17:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.04,0:17:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…就照办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打搅了～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.90,0:18:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细想想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我们打了这么久交道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.94,0:18:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是第一次来你房间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.99,0:18:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.57,0:18:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这么整洁 我吃惊了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.90,0:18:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我房间会是什么样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是更加…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.11,0:18:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 还是别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.48,0:18:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.96,0:18:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.42,0:18:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.30,0:18:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.87,0:18:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 老哥今年不去阿梅家过夜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.83,0:18:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.06,0:18:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才好像听到了别人的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.89,0:19:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道老哥你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.81,0:19:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算藏着 也瞒不过我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.89,0:19:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为单身过圣诞节寂寞 就看宝贝视频
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.41,0:19:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.59,0:19:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音小点哦 我要睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.39,0:19:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然安全过关 这挫败感是咋回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.34,0:19:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善解人意的好妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.57,0:19:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 宝贝视频是说这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.63,0:19:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过话说回来 你房间的壁橱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥会有星星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.56,0:19:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 因为这是我珍藏之地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.89,0:19:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这壁橱？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.79,0:19:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.64,0:19:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话好怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.61,0:19:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.95,0:19:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要帮你舔舔伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.17,0:19:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.90,0:19:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一起睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.07,0:19:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是开玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.99,0:19:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.64,0:19:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我不睡地板
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.99,0:20:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的一起睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.75,0:20:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事啦 不就是睡在旁边嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.95,0:20:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上赶在美也醒来前就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.09,0:20:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我睡壁橱啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.26,0:20:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起睡嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.47,0:20:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不过这实在有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你看看比星星更棒的东西～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.81,0:20:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.30,0:20:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.02,0:20:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.92,0:20:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是心跳加速的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.83,0:20:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之要冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.68,0:20:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 睡在身后的是美也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是美也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是睡相丑得无以复加
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.56,0:20:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还时常流口水的美也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.60,0:20:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么想吧 一定要这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.83,0:20:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.88,0:20:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥薰能睡得着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看她的睡相应该没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你醒着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.09,0:21:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 刚才在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.07,0:21:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想什么嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.07,0:21:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.79,0:21:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰 好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.45,0:21:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡着了？不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.48,0:21:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 薰 你没睡着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.46,0:21:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//--------------------------以下取自萌月字幕组出品BDRip字幕----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.68,0:22:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪都化了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.69,0:22:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.82,0:22:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果一夜没睡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.02,0:22:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 你还在骑这辆自行车啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.49,0:22:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是我的爱车啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.34,0:22:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中学的时候骑着它跑了很多地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.09,0:22:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.07,0:22:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人经常一起出去玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.54,0:22:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快乐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.88,0:22:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.03,0:22:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这以后也会一直快乐吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//--------------------------以上取自萌月字幕组出品BDRip字幕----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.39,0:22:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.38,0:22:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的关系也进一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.50,0:22:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更多更欢乐的事情 还在前面等着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.24,0:22:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//--------------------------以下取自萌月字幕组出品BDRip字幕----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.25,0:22:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后也要拜托你载我了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.65,0:22:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.89,0:22:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是温柔小子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.84,0:22:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰一会想去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.99,0:22:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.58,0:22:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工之前还有点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.25,0:22:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是先回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.86,0:22:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天都没有睡好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.45,0:22:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.32,0:22:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.80,0:22:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 难道你趁我睡着的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.31,0:22:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都没做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.10,0:23:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.99,0:23:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.44,0:23:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你好好抓紧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.56,0:23:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.00,0:23:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真危险
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.02,0:23:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你叫我抓紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.77,0:23:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放...放开点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.04,0:23:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 才不放开呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.23,0:23:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//--------------------------以上取自萌月字幕组出品BDRip字幕----------------------------
Comment: 0,0:00:28.00,0:00:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------NEXT-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.01,0:24:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集预告
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.72,0:24:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集开始 就是中多登场了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.20,0:25:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 我…我叫中多纱江 15岁
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.25,0:25:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.60,0:25:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中多
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.77,0:25:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才开始就这么紧张 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.27,0:25:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我会加油…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.73,0:25:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 学妹
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.91,0:25:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天邂逅的少年与少女
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.98,0:25:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正逐渐卷入恋爱的齿轮
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.70,0:25:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱的…齿轮
